These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, salsa, funk, r&b, hip-hop
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, turquise, purple, emerald, orange
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily, amaryllis, sunflower, tulip
 1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 2. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is the fan of pop##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the person who likes turquise and the fan of hip-hop##2
12. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
13. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | salsa      | r&b | hip-hop   | pop    |
| Color   | emerald  | turquise     | chestnut | purple | orange  |
| Flower           | lily | amaryllis      | tulip     | sunflower   | poppy     |

