.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
There 5 different types of food: pomegranate, broccoli, cranberry, zucchini, grapes
The people have 5 different jobs:  pilot, firefighter, chef, musician, accountant
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, tulip, orchid, daisy
 1. the person who growsdaisy is in the middle##1
 2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the firefighter##1
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the pilot and the person eating grapes##2
 6. the person who growsorchid is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the chef is the person eating zucchini##1
 9. the chef is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
11. the chef is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | gardening | writing    | hiking  | reading    |
| Food   | grapes    | broccoli       | cranberry      | pomegranate | zucchini        |
| Job   | accountant   | firefighter     | pilot    | musician  | chef     |
| Flower     | tulip    | amaryllis | daisy | orchid | sunflower |

