.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
There 5 different types of food: papaya, onion, nectarine, lettuce, lime
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, alhambra, montecristo, fonseca, siglo
House: victorian, modern, wooden, gothic-revival, art-deco
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the alhambra-smoker##1
 2. the gothic-revival house is in the middle##1
 3. the fonseca-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the person eating papaya is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the modern house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 7. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the wooden house##1
 8. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 9. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the victorian house is the person eating lettuce##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the art-deco house##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
13. the art-deco house is between the person eating lime and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Food   | lime  | onion | papaya | lettuce | nectarine        |
| Cigar   | montecristo      | alhambra      | fonseca       | siglo       | bongani       |
| House         | modern | art-deco  | gothic-revival    | victorian    | wooden        |

