.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
House: ranch-style, futuristic, modern, craftsman, colonial
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: weightlifting, rowing, basketball, water-polo, baseball
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, red, purple, fuchsia, turquise
 1. the person who likes red is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the futuristic house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 4. the person who likes turquise is between the fan of reggae and the craftsman house##2
 5. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the modern house##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the person who likes chestnut##1
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
12. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| House          | colonial  | modern     | craftsman   | futuristic     | ranch-style |
| Sport         | baseball | weightlifting    | basketball  | water-polo | rowing   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Color   | red    | purple | fuchsia | turquise | chestnut   |

