.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, lemonade, milk, mirinda
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: r&b, techno, salsa, pop, jazz
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, may, april, october, november
5 different pets are kept: rat, hamster, frog, goat, lizard
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 2. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the owner of the hamster and the fan of r&b##2
 5. the fan of jazz is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
12. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
13. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | milk       | mirinda       | almond-milk   | lemonade      | juice    |
| Music-Genre       | jazz | pop        | r&b       | salsa       | techno |
| Birthday        | november     | may        | october | march        | april  |
| Pet      | goat | frog | rat      | lizard | hamster  |

