 9. the owner of the pony is the social-worker##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the right of the electrician##1
12. the owner of the dog is the person who's birthday is in december##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
