.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, ritmeester, vegafina, game, siglo
There are 5 different nationalities: egyptian, brazilian, italian, chinese, spanish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball, sailing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, epic, documentary, superhero, crime
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person watching epic movies and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is the chinese##1
 4. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 6. the chinese is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the italian is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 9. the egyptian is on the left of the italian##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the person watching documentary movies is between the person who's sport is golf and the italian##2
12. the game-smoker is on the right of the spanish##1
13. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar    | vegafina       | game    | siglo | ritmeester  | dannemann        |
| Nationality       | spanish | egyptian | italian  | chinese | brazilian    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero       | documentary      | crime      | fantasy | epic  |

