.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
5 different pets are kept: lizard, cat, guinea-pig, bird, hedgehog
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, entrepreneur, fisherman, pilot
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, badminton, lacrosse, water-polo, rugby
House: farmhouse, modern, art-deco, ranch-style, palace
 1. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 2. the fisherman is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the entrepreneur##2
 3. the owner of the bird is the fisherman##1
 4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
 6. the owner of the bird is between the pilot and the modern house##2
 7. the ranch-style house is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is the art-deco house##1
 9. the farmhouse house is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
11. the entrepreneur is the person who's sport is badminton##1
12. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Pet      | lizard      | cat         | bird      | guinea-pig | hedgehog     |
| Job           | engineer | entrepreneur | fisherman | pilot    | bartender  |
| Sport   | water-polo  | badminton    | surfing | lacrosse    | rugby |
| House   | art-deco  | modern        | farmhouse   | ranch-style    | palace     |

