.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, tower, ranch-style, wooden
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, may, march, september, june
There 5 different types of food: pomegranate, apricot, cherry, cabbage, zucchini
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the wooden house is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating apricot is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person eating pomegranate##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
 7. the tower house is between the person driving the airplane and the wooden house##2
 8. the farmhouse house is between the ranch-style house and the gothic-revival house##2
 9. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
10. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| House         | wooden  | tower | ranch-style   | farmhouse      | gothic-revival |
| Birthday   | april   | september    | may | june | march      |
| Food           | cherry | apricot    | pomegranate       | cabbage     | zucchini      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

