.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
There 5 different types of food: watermelon, plum, carrot, nizza-climbing, kiwi
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
City: miami, san-francisco, paris, rome, nizza
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, iced-tea, milk, 7up
 1. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person drinking milk and the person traveling to nizza##2
 3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the person traveling to miami##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is between the person drinking 7up and the person traveling to paris##2
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person traveling to rome##1
 8. the person eating nizza-climbing is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person drinking tea is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
10. the person eating nizza-climbing is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person eating plum##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Food         | carrot    | kiwi  | plum  | watermelon      | nizza-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| City   | paris | miami    | nizza    | rome       | san-francisco         |
| Beverage   | milk  | almond-milk | 7up    | iced-tea     | tea      |

 